      <title>10 Bash Scripting Tips for Everyday DevOps</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/javaops/posts/bash-tips/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/javaops/posts/bash-tips/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Bash scripting is a powerful skill for any developer or DevOps engineer. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re automating deployments, setting up environments, or writing health checks, here are &lt;strong&gt;10 useful Bash tips and tricks&lt;/strong&gt; to level up your scripting game.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-set--e-and--u-for-safer-scripts&#34;&gt;1️⃣ Set &lt;code&gt;-e&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;-u&lt;/code&gt; for Safer Scripts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;#!/bin/bash
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;set -eu
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;-e: Exit on error&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;-u: Treat unset variables as errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use this at the top of your scripts for better safety.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
